* Init Scripts
** Runs during cluster startup
***_ Before Spark driver starts
***_ Every time cluster starts
** Use cases
***_ System packages (apt-get)
***_ Environment variables
***_ Monitoring agents
***_ System-level config
** Not recommended for library install
***_ Use cluster-scoped libraries instead
** Storage
***_ Unity Catalog volumes (DBR 13.3+)
***_ Path: /Volumes/main/eng/scripts/setup.sh
** Standard access mode
***_ Init script path must be in allowlist
** Failure behavior
***_ Non-zero exit code = cluster fails to start
***_ Enables troubleshooting via cluster logs
** Use as last resort
***_ Prefer cluster policies and cluster-scoped libs
@endmindmap
